<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1303119>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Adults of I. ventalloi. A, male dorsal; B, male ventral. Bar length for A and B: 1.5 mm. C, male, spiracular plate. D, male, gnathosoma, dorsal view; E, male, gnathosoma, ventral view. Bar length for D and E: 0.25 mm. F, male, hypostome. G, male, coxae and trochanters I to IV. H, female dorsal; I, female ventral. Bar length for A and B: 1.5 mm. J, female, spiracular plate. K, female, gnathosoma, dorsal view; L, female, gnathosoma, ventral view. Bar length for K and L: 0.25 mm. M, female, hypostome. N, female, coxae and trochanters I to IV." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1303119/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1303121>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Immatures of I. ventalloi. A, nymph dorsal; B, nymph ventral. Bar length for A, B: 0.6 mm. C, nymph, spiracular plate. D, nymph, gnathosoma, dorsal view; E, nymph, gnathosoma, ventral view. Bar length for C, D: 0.3 mm. F, nymph, hypostome. G, nymph, coxae and trochanters I to IV. H, larva dorsal; I, larva ventral. Bar length for G and H: 0.4 mm. J, larva, gnathosoma, dorsal view; K, larva, gnathosoma, ventral view. Bar length for I, J: 0.2 mm. L, larva, hypostome. M, larva, coxae and trochanters I to IV." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1303121/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1303123>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Phylogenetic tree for I. ventalloi based on 16S rDNA." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1303123/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

